10.00	Viva_la_Vida_Tour	Viva la Vida Tour	The Viva la Vida Tour was the fourth concert tour by British band Coldplay. The tour was in support their fourth studio album Viva la Vida or Death and All His Friends (2008). The tour was a massive commercial and critical success visiting Europe, Asia, the Americas and Australasia. The tour further established the band as one the concert industry's biggest draws and as one of the world's most popular bands.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2c/Thevivalavidatour.jpg/220px-Thevivalavidatour.jpg
